Definition: a story that appears mysteriously and spreads spontaneously in various forms and is usually false
Example: contains elements of humor or horror and is popularly believed to be true
Synonyms: report, a, story, that, appears, mysteriously, and, spreads, spontaneously, in, various, forms, is, usually, false, contains, elements, of, humor, or, horror, popularly, believed, to, be, true
Category: noun.communication
